                Player: My Familiar looks so much better. You've done a great job at healing them.
                Roy: ...
                Roy: Thanks {$playerName}. That means a lot.
                Roy: You know, meeting you today has really given me lots to think about.
                Roy: I'll maybe see you around.
                Player: Hopefully I'll see you again sometime.
            -> Player: To be honest, I don't really care. 
                Player: Can you just heal my Familiar?
                Player: ...
                Player: Erm... Hello?
                Roy: Do you want me to heal your Familiar or not?
    -> Player: Can you cheer up a bit?
        Roy: ...
        Roy: Do you want me to heal your Familiar up or not?
===

