title: chapter1_npc_villager1_and_2
tags:
---
Matilda: Have you heard of all the goings on in the news? The StopIt! Militia is at it again. It's all anyone's talking about.
Christa: Terrible, isn't it? Kidnapping people's Familiars is just awful. I don't know what I'd do if someone took mine.
